{"thag5.9:0.1":"Theragatha 5.9 ","thag5.9:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","thag5.9:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag5.9:0.4":"Vijitasenattheragatha ","thag5.9:1.1":"“Olaggessami te citta, ","thag5.9:1.2":"anidvareva hatthinam; ","thag5.9:1.3":"Na tam pape niyojessam, ","thag5.9:1.4":"kamajala sariraja. ","thag5.9:2.1":"Tvam olaggo na gacchasi, ","thag5.9:2.2":"Dvaravivaram gajova alabhanto; ","thag5.9:2.3":"Na ca cittakali punappunam, ","thag5.9:2.4":"Pasakka paparato carissasi. ","thag5.9:3.1":"Yatha kunjaram adantam, ","thag5.9:3.2":"Navaggahamankusaggaho; ","thag5.9:3.3":"Balava avatteti akamam, ","thag5.9:3.4":"Evam avattayissam tam. ","thag5.9:4.1":"Yatha varahayadamakusalo, ","thag5.9:4.2":"Sarathi pavaro dameti ajannam; ","thag5.9:4.3":"Evam damayissam tam, ","thag5.9:4.4":"Patitthito pancasu balesu. ","thag5.9:5.1":"Satiya tam nibandhissam, ","thag5.9:5.2":"Payutto te damessami; ","thag5.9:5.3":"Viriyadhuraniggahito, ","thag5.9:5.4":"Na yito duram gamissase citta”ti. ","thag5.9:5.5":"… Vijitaseno thero …. "}